# Repository profile

- Package manager: Bun
- Workspace paths: `apps/*`, `packages/*`
- Package namespace: `__SCOPE__/*`
- Source condition: `__SOURCE_CONDITION__`
- Compiled package command: `tsc -p tsconfig.build.json`
- Aggregate proof: `bun run verification`
- Documentation router: `docs/README.md`
- Documentation registry: `docs/documentation-map.json`
- Architecture owner: `ARCHITECTURE.md` and `docs/architecture/`
- Runbook owner: `docs/runbooks/`
- Critical-journey owner: `docs/critical-journeys/journeys.json`
- Proof owner: `docs/proof/`
- Authority/control owner: `docs/governance/`
- Evidence/archive owner: `docs/evidence/`
- Documentation checks: repository structural validator, then aggregate proof
- README rule: summarize and route; do not become a second semantic owner
- Generated/reference owner: generators and lockfiles remain tool-owned; record digests in the render receipt
- Mirror policy: repository-local skills are portable projections; repository docs remain canonical for local facts
- Generated/forbidden writes: `node_modules`, `dist`, `.output`, `.turbo`, and
  generated `routeTree.gen.ts`
